data.description: Welcome to this fantastic investment opportunity! This multifamily unit is nestled on a generous .81-acre plot of land, offering plenty of space and potential for various uses. Property A boasts a comfortable 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom house, providing a cozy and inviting living space. Property B complements it with an apartment featuring 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom. One of the standout features of this property is the expansive carport, capable of sheltering up to 7 cars. The backyard offers a large pool, though currently inoperable, rest assured it can be restored to its former glory with proper care and attention. The property includes a kitchenette and bathroom, which require some repair work. As an investor's dream, this property is currently tenant-occupied, providing a steady income stream. Moreover, the mixed residential zoning allows for a myriad of possibilities. Whether you wish to continue its current use or explore the potential of turning it into a commercial property.
